{"tid":1671971,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"轉發：【超合作運動：攬炒繳費機械人】","createTime":"2019-10-23T23:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T21:21:01.000Z","uid":300018,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cc36216142bbde44623eb4311b39b3430dafd9bb","tid":1671971,"uid":300018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:49:26.000Z","msg":"原po<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kkfly.hk/videos/509057066613243?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkkfly.hk%2Fvideos%2F509057066613243%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=2e88cdb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kkfly.hk/videos/509057066613243?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【超合作運動：攬炒繳費機械人🤖】<br />\n🏛交稅手續費「食窮」政府、「逐蚊」交稅政府每次蝕1倍🤗<br />\n👮&zwj;♂️交差餉俾Popo買催淚彈定買多架水炮車？還是想出OT俾佢打完人買iPhone？「逐蚊」交差餉政府每次蝕1倍😏<br />\n🚇住黨鐵物業養肥黨鐵又成日罷駛？「逐蚊」交管理費黨鐵每次蝕1倍😎<br />\n<br />\n原理：商戶與PPS的合約，每次以PPS交費、不論交易金額商戶均支付$2元手續費<br />\n策略：每次市民交$1、商戶要俾$2「倍蝕」給PPS💸💸💸<br />\n困難：以人手操作交一萬幾千、撳到手斷都未交完🤯<br />\n解決：朋友早在14年雨革已經開發了自動交稅機，當時只得Windows版，今年有人參考他的方法，開發了MAC版。這些版本都要在電腦上執行，大家或許對電腦操作不太熟悉或擔心個人資料被盜。有見及此，我們將攬炒繳費🤖加入KKFly 手機app，幾個Steps，其他就交俾機械人🤖<br />\n應用：稅、差餉、地租、水費、Grant Loan (學生償還貸款)、Autotoll、黨鐵管理費<br />\n大部份接受PPS繳費的服務也可使用。記住你交$1，佢要倒貼$1，如果唔係十冤九仇就唔好用！<br />\n<br />\n⚠️合法同極權攬炒！係香港人就Share開去！✊🏻<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可 #香港人反抗 #一蚊稅💸💸💸<br />\n<br />\n【公民抗命】教你如何合法交稅/差餉/水費交到政府蝕錢 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1637669\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1637669</a><br />\n<br />\n1️⃣有無風險？<br />\n2014年仲有「不誠實取用電腦」，但2019年條例已經廢咗，只要你係用你自己部電腦就唔犯法。PPS 及法例都無規定你唔可以手動不停咁交一蚊。<br />\n2️⃣用 PPS 交其實同用支票交有無分別？<br />\n用支票要逐張入比較麻煩，開幾千張支票就算用印章都做到手軟。上網交可以全自動進行，方便啲。正常商戶每條 PPS 過數會被收取2蚊手續費，所以理論上你交嘅錢會全部變成手續費，商戶仲要倒貼。<br />\n3️⃣有無毒 / 伏？<br />\n所有登入資料不會被我方讀取或上傳。KKFly開始咗一年幾，好多人用KKFly以信用卡購買演唱會門票。如果要盜用，唔會等而家先偷你的PPS。KKFly app只在App Store及Google Play上架，切勿以其他途徑安裝。<br />\n<br />\n使用教學🤖<a href=\"http://bit.ly/pps111bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fpps111bot&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=bd403d07\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/pps111bot</a><br />\n準備繳費靈戶口：攜同提款卡到就近OK便利店開戶口。<br />\n下載KKFly app：<br />\niOS： <a href=\"https://apple.co/2kAUTHj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2kAUTHj&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=9b214672\" target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2kAUTHj</a><br />\nAndroid： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IZuQYY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IZuQYY&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=23771f50\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IZuQYY</a><br />\n使用步驟、詳細教學：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/pps111bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fpps111bot&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=bd403d07\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/pps111bot</a>"},{"pid":"0d55b680b14c601a7ff9ab5e73566f4de438970c","tid":1671971,"uid":300018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:49:39.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"ecb316dcfe75bcca578fbe4a2ce2f0dcb6f92ff5","tid":1671971,"uid":300018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:49:49.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"51885fabe5ba7c3b4b584ff6f0b197485c0c6a31","tid":1671971,"uid":300018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:50:03.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"49b6250054529ba40b68fa82eb51b844cf116e6a","tid":1671971,"uid":300018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:50:13.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"4641d21cc3d62a507fa8285d74801aef4a1e5934","tid":1671971,"uid":300018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:50:26.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"1cb3a5e1d08132e52809369dbf1a9f7f269dbb9a","tid":1671971,"uid":300018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T23:50:40.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":